title: Paddington Bear heads to St Paul's in late author's last work
text:
Paddington Bear heads to St Paul's in late author's last work 10:21pm IST - 01:53
The marmalade-loving bear visits the famed London site where he is mistaken for a member of the choir in 'Paddington at St Paul's' by Michael Bond. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
